[Mar 5, Harare]
Zimbabwe     2-1 Lesotho
  [Joel Lupahla 69, Mpitsa Marai 89og; Masupha Majara 9]
[Mar 25, Lusaka]
Zambia       3-0 Botswana
  [Mark Sinyangwe 7, Harry Milanzi 32, Chaswe Nsofwa 89]
[Apr 15, Blantyre]
Malawi       2-1 Mozambique
  [Daniel Chitsulo 5, Mike Kumanga 9; Amide 58]
[Apr 29, Phokeng]
South Africa 3-0 Mauritius
  [Patrick Mayo 13pen, Godfrey Sapula 69, Siyabonga Nomvete 78]

*byes: Angola (holders), Namibia, Swaziland 
*best losers: Lesotho (on better disciplinary record compared to Mozambique)

*NB: Seychelles and Madagascar registered for the tournament following their
*    admission to COSAFA (like Mauritius) but were excluded from participation
*    due to 'budgetary constraints'.

